  "Bulk movement of fluid carrying thermal energy": "",
  "Electromagnetic waves": "",
  "Electron flow in metals": "",
  "Molecular vibrations in solids": "",
  "Convection occurs when warmer, less dense fluid rises and cooler, denser fluid sinks, creating circulation that transfers thermal energy.": "",
