  "The rate of cooling is proportional to the square of the temperature difference": "",
  "Cooling only occurs through radiation": "",
  "All objects cool at the same rate": "",
  "Newton's law of cooling: dT/dt = -h(T - T_env). The rate of temperature change is proportional to the temperature difference.": "",
